  }, "v9"), mdx("p", null, "C\xF3 l\u1EDDi ph\xE1n cho c\xE1c nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri: Ta \u0111au l\xF2ng l\u1EAFm. X\u01B0\u01A1ng c\u1ED1t ta run r\u1EA9y. Ta gi\u1ED1ng nh\u01B0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi say, nh\u01B0 k\u1EBB say r\u01B0\u1EE3u v\xEC CH\xDAA v\xE0 v\xEC l\u1EDDi th\xE1nh c\u1EE7a Ng\xE0i. "), mdx("h6", {
