  }, "v13"), mdx("p", null, "\"Ta \u0111\xE3 th\u1EA5y c\xE1c ti\xEAn tri trong Xa-ma-ri l\xE0m b\u1EADy. C\xE1c ti\xEAn tri \u0111\xF3 n\xF3i ti\xEAn tri nh\xE2n danh Ba-anh v\xE0 d\u1EABn d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en \u0111i sai l\u1EA1c. "), mdx("h6", {
