  }, "v20"), mdx("p", null, "C\u01A1n gi\u1EADn Ng\xE0i kh\xF4ng ngu\xF4i cho \u0111\u1EBFn khi Ng\xE0i ho\xE0n th\xE0nh \u0111i\u1EC1u Ng\xE0i \u0111\u1ECBnh l\xE0m. Khi ng\xE0y \u1EA5y xong r\u1ED3i, th\xEC c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i s\u1EBD hi\u1EC3u r\xF5 \u0111i\u1EC1u n\u1EA7y. "), mdx("h6", {
