    "id": "v26"
  }, "v26"), mdx("p", null, "Chuy\u1EC7n \u0111\xF3 c\xF2n \u1EDF trong \u0111\u1EA7u c\u1EE7a c\xE1c nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri d\u1ED1i tr\xE1 \u0111\xF3 bao l\xE2u n\u1EEFa? Ch\xFAng n\xF3i ti\xEAn tri do tr\xED t\u01B0\u1EDFng t\u01B0\u1EE3ng c\u1EE7a m\xECnh. "), mdx("h6", {
